{"tid":809110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"引用匿名評論 《紐時》公信力大賭注","createTime":"2018-09-07T01:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T11:09:04.000Z","uid":20816,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1f290487a467a17bfbde786bab2f48ec1d7352a5","tid":809110,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T01:58:40.000Z","msg":"《紐約時報》在評論專欄刊出一篇自稱為白宮高層宮員的匿名來函，做法罕見及極具風險。但該報發言人指這是「唯一可將此重要角度帶給讀者」的做法。<br />\n<br />\n三名高層下決定<br />\n<br />\n《紐時》專欄編輯達奧（James Dao）指，上周透過中間人收到文章，編輯們是在有信心已確認撰文者身份後，才開綠燈。除了達奧，社論版編輯貝內特（James Bennet）及出版人蘇茲貝格（A.G. Sulzberger）都有參與決定。<br />\n達奧指文章單憑內容的重要性，已足以獲刊，又形容做法雖然罕見，但並非無先例。該報今年中刊登一篇身在看守所的難民所撰之文章時，也因作者曾受非法集團威脅，無公開其身份。<br />\n有該報記者則指事件使他陷角色衝突，記者康托爾（Jodi Kantor）反問「《紐時》記者應該嘗試揭露那專欄版同事發誓要保障作者身份嗎？」<br />\n有線新聞網絡（CNN）華盛頓分社前社長、喬治華盛頓大學媒體與公共事務學院院長塞斯諾（Frank Sesno）更指無法想像《紐時》作此決定，認為「一間負責任的新聞機構不會這樣做」。他解釋若撰文者只是普通人，《紐時》的公信力將岌岌可危。<br />\n美聯社<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180907/20493757\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180907%2F20493757&d=Lef8AG442bpl9RNJhf0ophv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=39298d91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180907%2F20493757&h=81c48865\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180907/20493757</a>"},{"pid":"275e817bfabfd3c0664e01f2aeb2e6591ef011d7","tid":809110,"uid":54502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T01:59:25.000Z","msg":"Fake news"},{"pid":"addcc7d72499ebf8ced576005b33e450d6e7e776","tid":809110,"uid":74379,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"同CCTVB既&quot;有分析認為&quot;有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e6d107b4c9ca357ad0ed5afe85679006b2ea49","tid":809110,"uid":39221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:47:10.000Z","msg":"篇評論講咩?"},{"pid":"5f067f8add375b6ffe848d44fb49d6dad2d6d814","tid":809110,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:51:37.000Z","msg":"呢間times已經比支拿入侵咗"},{"pid":"b60344bfe51f5c03b4ece93f1a249b81855433a3","tid":809110,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4e6d107b4c9ca357ad0ed5afe85679006b2ea49","tid":809110,"uid":39221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:47:10.000Z","msg":"篇評論講咩?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T03:00:40.000Z","msg":"呢篇文章？<br />\n<br />\n匿名官員稱美國內閣曾考慮把特朗普趕下台<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bzcyiS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bzcyiS</a>"},{"pid":"1e87488db4303951afe543d115635bbc073f4536","tid":809110,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"addcc7d72499ebf8ced576005b33e450d6e7e776","tid":809110,"uid":74379,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"同CCTVB既&quot;有分析認為&quot;有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T03:39:11.000Z","msg":"CCTVB尻噏冇成本，人地就用報社信譽背書。"},{"pid":"99064b966ae2c4dd68422bf214c7047f63686a28","tid":809110,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T08:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34e3a7e5750d2b6f3fd50496fc7039ccf36cf4b","tid":809110,"uid":14449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:00:11.000Z","msg":"Fake news 末日"},{"pid":"866039451b6655d63076d98f6965f635bcf636dc","tid":809110,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T11:09:04.000Z","msg":"如果侵侵之後走出黎話篇文章係佢寫會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}